description: In outline, but inclusive of full details of matters of scale, layout and access, a phased redevelopment of the site comprising of: the demolition of the 390 existing residential dwellings and the existing community centre; the erection of 525 new residential dwellings within six blocks in total, ranging from 5 to 9 storeys in height; the provision of a new 800 sqm community centre (use class D1); the installation of a combined heat and power plant; and improvements to the public realm with new streets, pedestrian routes, amenity spaces and children's play spaces, together with the provision of car and cycle parking spaces.
